{"title":"企业标准的开发环境搭建","date":"2020-04-03T00:00:00.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Apr 3, 2020","L":"04/03/2020","MM-DD":"04-03"},"updated":"2024-07-01T17:57:02.542Z","content":"<p><strong><a href=\"https://www.imooc.com/\" target=\"_blank\">慕课网</a>实战课程笔记 —— <a href=\"https://class.imooc.com/sc/70/learn\" target=\"_blank\">大前端：前端全栈加强版！前端全栈+全周期+多端（升级Vue3.0）</a></strong></p>\n<h2 id=\"开发环境\">开发环境<a title=\"#开发环境\" href=\"#开发环境\"></a></h2>\n<p>开发环境准备</p>\n<ul>\n<li>本地环境\n<ul>\n<li>Node.js</li>\n<li>IDE</li>\n<li>Vue-CLi</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>测试环境\n<ul>\n<li>Linux</li>\n<li>Docker</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>数据库服务\n<ul>\n<li>MongoDB</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>本地环境</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Node.js (npm/yarn) + nvm(Node.js版本管理)</li>\n<li>IDE(Webstorm/VScode/Atom)</li>\n<li>Vue-CLi\n<ul>\n<li>安装命令: npm install -g @vue/cli</li>\n<li>快速原型开发: npm install -g @vue/cli-service-global</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>测试环境</p>\n<ul>\n<li>虚拟机自建环境（Parallels/Vmware/Hyperv）</li>\n<li>购买云服务</li>\n<li>安装Docker</li>\n</ul>\n<p>包管理工具</p>\n<ul>\n<li>npm, cnpm\n<ul>\n<li>安装命令: npm install -g cnpm --registry=<a href=\"https://registry.npm.taobao.org\" target=\"_blank\">https://registry.npm.taobao.org</a></li>\n<li>官方网址: <a href=\"https://npm.taobao.org\" target=\"_blank\">https://npm.taobao.org</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Yarn\n<ul>\n<li>官方网址: <a href=\"https://yarnpkg.com\" target=\"_blank\">https://yarnpkg.com</a></li>\n<li>常用命令: yarn add/install/remove</li>\n<li>下载地址: <a href=\"https://github.com/yarnpkg/yarn/releases\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/yarnpkg/yarn/releases</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>开发系统环境介绍</p>\n<p>linux 常用命令：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>lsb_release -a</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>uname -a</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>df -Th</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>top</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>文档型：文件相关命令 (touch, cat, echo, rm, vi, cd)</p>\n<ul>\n<li>mkdir testdir</li>\n<li>touch test.txt</li>\n<li>vi test.txt // I 输入，esc退出，:wq/:q!</li>\n<li>echo ‘123’ &gt;&gt; test.txt</li>\n<li>echo ‘hello world’ &gt; test.txt</li>\n<li>cat test.txt</li>\n<li>rm test.txt</li>\n<li>rm -r testdir/</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>硬件型：磁盘/进程/服务/网络</p>\n<ul>\n<li>ps -ef | grep docker</li>\n<li>service sshd status/stop/restart</li>\n<li>systermctl status firewalld.service</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>功能型：压缩/解压，下载，远程</p>\n<ul>\n<li>wget [url]</li>\n<li>tar zxvf [filename]</li>\n<li>tar zcvf [.gz filename] [filename]</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>SSH密钥远程连接</p>\n<ul>\n<li>service sshd status  // ubuntu 是 ssh</li>\n<li>netstat -anlp | grep sshd</li>\n<li>vi /etc/ssh/sshd_config</li>\n<li>semanage port -a -t ssh_port_t -p tcp 10022</li>\n<li>yum whatprovides semanage</li>\n<li>yum install -y policycoreutils-python</li>\n<li>semanage port -l | grep ssh</li>\n<li>semanage port -d -t ssh_port_t -p tcp [端口号]</li>\n<li>service sshd restart</li>\n</ul>\n<p>将电脑的公钥复制到服务器的 ～.ssh/authorized_keys 文件中</p>\n<p>Docker主要特性</p>\n<ul>\n<li>文件、资源、网络隔离</li>\n<li>变更管理、日志记录</li>\n<li>写时复制</li>\n</ul>\n<p>安装Docker<br>\n<a href=\"https://docs.docker.com/install/linux/docker-ce/centos/\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.docker.com/install/linux/docker-ce/centos/</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li>systemctl start docker</li>\n<li>docker run hello-world</li>\n<li>docker ps (-a)</li>\n</ul>\n<p>添加国内源</p>\n<ul>\n<li>vi /etc/docker/daemon.json</li>\n<li>systemctl daemon-reload</li>\n<li>systemctl restart docker</li>\n<li>docker rm [id/name]</li>\n<li>docker stop [id/name]</li>\n</ul>\n<p>容器化应用</p>\n<p>Docker Compose</p>\n<ul>\n<li>sudo curl -L “<a href=\"https://github.com/docker/compose/releases/download/1.25.4/docker-compose-$\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/docker/compose/releases/download/1.25.4/docker-compose-$</a>(uname -s)-$(uname -m)” -o /usr/local/bin/docker-compose</li>\n<li>curl -L <a href=\"https://get.daocloud.io/docker/compose/releases/download/1.25.4/docker-compose-%60uname\" target=\"_blank\">https://get.daocloud.io/docker/compose/releases/download/1.25.4/docker-compose-`uname</a> -s<code>-</code>uname -m` &gt; /usr/local/bin/docker-compose</li>\n<li>sudo chmod +x /usr/local/bin/docker-compose</li>\n<li>vi docker-compose.yml</li>\n<li>docker compose up -d</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight yml\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">version:</span> <span class=\"string\">&#x27;3&#x27;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">services:</span> </span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attr\">mysql1:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">image:</span> <span class=\"string\">mysql</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">environment:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"bullet\">-</span> <span class=\"attr\">MYSQL_ROOT_PASSWORD:</span> <span class=\"number\">123456</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">ports:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"bullet\">-</span> <span class=\"number\">28002</span><span class=\"string\">:3306</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attr\">mysql2:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">image:</span> <span class=\"string\">mysql</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">environment:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"bullet\">-</span> <span class=\"attr\">MYSQL_ROOT_PASSWORD:</span> <span class=\"number\">123456</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">ports:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"bullet\">-</span> <span class=\"number\">28003</span><span class=\"string\">:3306</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>Docker常问题</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>常见命令 (run/start/stop/restart/log)</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>docker-compose集成命令</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Docker仓库 (Docker hub 及私有仓库 Harbor)</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>docker login</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>docker pull/push</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>认识 Node.js</p>\n<ul>\n<li>免费、开源、跨平台</li>\n<li>服务器上的JavaScript<strong>运行环境</strong></li>\n<li>基于Chrome V8引擎，<strong>事件驱动、非阻塞式I/O</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p>包管理工具</p>\n<ul>\n<li>npm, cnpm\n<ul>\n<li>安装命令: npm install -g cnpm --registry=<a href=\"https://registry.npm.taobao.org\" target=\"_blank\">https://registry.npm.taobao.org</a></li>\n<li>官方网址: <a href=\"https://npm.taobao.org\" target=\"_blank\">https://npm.taobao.org</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Yarn\n<ul>\n<li>官方网址: <a href=\"https://yarnpkg.com\" target=\"_blank\">https://yarnpkg.com</a></li>\n<li>常用命令: yarn add/install/remove</li>\n<li>下载地址: <a href=\"https://github.com/yarnpkg/yarn/releases\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/yarnpkg/yarn/releases</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>RESTful API</p>\n<p>representational state transfer 表现层状态转移</p>\n<p>特点</p>\n<ul>\n<li>客户端-服务端</li>\n<li>无状态-可缓存</li>\n<li>统一接口</li>\n</ul>\n<p>本地安装接口测试工具</p>\n<p>Mock数据开发流程</p>\n<ol>\n<li>前端定义接口</li>\n<li>完成静态页面</li>\n<li>完成UI交互</li>\n<li>对接真实接口</li>\n<li>页面/逻辑测试</li>\n<li>线上部署</li>\n</ol>\n<p>docker-compose 安装 doclever</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight yml\"><figcaption><span>/home/doclever/docker-compose.yml</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">version:</span> <span class=\"string\">&quot;2&quot;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">services:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attr\">DOClever:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">image:</span> <span class=\"string\">lw96/doclever</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">restart:</span> <span class=\"string\">always</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">container_name:</span> <span class=\"string\">&quot;DOClever&quot;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">ports:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"bullet\">-</span> <span class=\"number\">20080</span><span class=\"string\">:10000</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">volumes:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"bullet\">-</span> <span class=\"string\">/srv/doclever/file:/root/DOClever/data/file</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"bullet\">-</span> <span class=\"string\">/srv/doclever/img:/root/DOClever/data/img</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"bullet\">-</span> <span class=\"string\">/srv/doclever/tmp:/root/DOClever/data/tmp</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">environment:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"bullet\">-</span> <span class=\"string\">DB_HOST=mongodb://mongo:27017/DOClever</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"bullet\">-</span> <span class=\"string\">PORT=10000</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">links:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"bullet\">-</span> <span class=\"string\">mongo:mongo</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attr\">mongo:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">image:</span> <span class=\"string\">mongo:latest</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">restart:</span> <span class=\"string\">always</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">container_name:</span> <span class=\"string\">&quot;mongodb&quot;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">volumes:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"bullet\">-</span> <span class=\"string\">/srv/doclever/db:/data/db</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li>docker-compose up -d // 拉取镜像创建服务</li>\n<li>docker ps ｜ grep doclever // 查看正在运行的容器</li>\n<li>firewall-cmd --state/–list-all</li>\n<li>firewall-cmd --add-port=20080/tcp --zone=public --permanent</li>\n<li>firewall-cmd --reload</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Mock.js 简介</p>\n<p>Webpack 核心概念</p>\n<ul>\n<li>入口：从哪个文件开始</li>\n<li>输出：</li>\n<li>Loader</li>\n<li>插件</li>\n<li>模式/兼容性</li>\n</ul>\n","link":"front_end/front_end_2","comments":true,"plink":"https://vincenteliang.com/front_end/front_end_2/","toc":[{"id":"开发环境","title":"开发环境","index":"1"}],"reward":true,"copyright":{"author":"Vincente Liang","link":"<a href=\"https://vincenteliang.com/front_end/front_end_2/\" title=\"企业标准的开发环境搭建\">https://vincenteliang.com/front_end/front_end_2/</a>","license":"Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives 4.0 International (<a href=\\\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/\\\" rel=\\\"external nofollow\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)","published":"April 3, 2020","updated":"July 1, 2024"}}